text: Józef Karpiel (18 January 1932 - 29 November 1994) was a Polish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:1994 deaths Category:Polish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Poland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:People from Tatra County
